{{Top|leg}}
'''Hyperbaric recharge globes''' were medical devices of unknown purposes. [[Wat Tambor/Legends|Wat Tambor]] used one to recover from his ordeal at the hands of the Republic during his captivity.

{{Tech-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
"Hyperbaric" refers to above-average pressure, suggesting that the hyperbaric recharge globe has to do with the Skakoans' need for high air pressure.

